"... either version 2 of the License, or (at your option) any later version..."

Finally, we have received express autorisations to release the only dependencies under
GNU GPL v2: D0 RunI and RunII cone plugins and ATLAScone code, 
under GNU GPL v3 or later license. Specifically, 
  - we received agreement from Joey Huston <Huston@pa.msu.edu> to distribute the ATLAScone code under GPL v3 or later;
  - we received agreement from Paul Grannis for the D0 collaboration to distribute the D0 RunI and RunII cone plugins under GPL v3 or later.

